            <p>There's lots more to learn about Old English syntax, but the features discussed in this module will
                give
                you the fundamentals needed to read Old English texts. That said, it is important to remember that these are not
                hard and fast rules. You will occasionally come across Subject-Verb word order in subordinate
                clauses, and short
                sentences with few conjunctions.
            </p>
